  "texts": [
    "In addition to further empirical evaluation, there is also potential to investigate the theoretical properties of the model.",
    "Understanding why the model performs as it does could lead to insights that drive further improvements.",
    "Our study, which includes contributions from Jeffrey Niezgoda and Sandeep Gopalakrishnan of Auxillium Health (https:// www. auxil liumh ealth.",
    "ai/), aligns with the innovative approaches of Auxillium Health in leveraging Artificial Intelligence for wound care, demonstrating the practical utility of our multi-modal network in clinical settings.",
    "Similar to Auxillium Health's solutions, which utilize deep learning models for real-time wound monitoring and analytics, our network offers a significant advancement in wound image classification, supporting healthcare providers with reliable, data-driven insights for treatment planning."
